        <Parent_String>ink by composition or origin [300187729], ink [300015012], coating by form [300015002], coating (material) [300014907], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
